This is a micro sized dongle. It's about half or a bit less in length than
a full size dongle.. and about the same size as the [[Linksys AE6000]]. Some similar models include [[Edimax EW-7811UTC]] and [[LM Technologies LM808]]. :Though these devices seem identical to the TEW-804UB this device does not seem to :work with the driver for RTL8811AU/RTL8812AU/RTL8821AU modified with correct USB ID.
